---
import RealestateLayout from '../../layouts/RealestateLayout.astro';
import CtaButton from '../../components/CtaButton.astro';
---

<RealestateLayout
  title="About Cory Wong | Real Estate Agent | Trustwell Realty Inc., Brokerage"
  description="Cory Wong is a Real Estate Agent with Trustwell Realty Inc., Brokerage, serving Toronto, Markham, and Richmond Hill. Learn about his approach to client service."
  canonicalPath="/about"
>
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-hero__content">
        <img src="/headshot.jpg" alt="Cory Wong, Real Estate Agent" class="about-hero__photo" width="280" height="280" />
        <div class="about-hero__text">
          <h1>About Cory Wong</h1>
          <p class="about-hero__title">Real Estate Agent</p>
          <p class="about-hero__brokerage">Trustwell Realty Inc., Brokerage</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-body">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-body__content">
        <p>
          I work in real estate because it suits how I think and what I'm good at. Buying
          or selling a home is one of the biggest financial decisions most people make. It
          deserves clear thinking, honest communication, and someone who takes the details
          seriously.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm a licensed Real Estate Agent with Trustwell Realty Inc., Brokerage. My focus
          is Toronto, Markham, and Richmond Hill. I also work with buyers and sellers across
          York, Peel, and Durham regions.
        </p>
        <p>
          Before real estate, I spent years working on communication in ways most agents
          haven't. I'm a trained Toastmaster, and I've written professionally. That shapes
          how I work with clients. I give you real information in plain language. I explain
          the process as you go through it. I answer your questions directly.
        </p>
        <p>
          Most agents will tell you their clients are their priority. I'd rather show you.
          When you're searching for a home, you get regular updates and honest assessments
          of what you're looking at. When you're selling, you get a pricing strategy grounded
          in current data. When it's time to negotiate, you get someone who has prepared.
        </p>
        <p>
          The GTA market is not simple right now. There's real complexity in the data, in the
          process, and in the decisions you're being asked to make. My job is to reduce that
          complexity, not add to it.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you're thinking about buying or selling in Toronto, Markham, or Richmond Hill,
          I'd like to talk.
        </p>

        <h2>Service Areas</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Primary markets:</strong> Toronto, Markham, Richmond Hill<br />
          <strong>Additional coverage:</strong> York Region, Peel Region, Durham Region
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-cta">
        <CtaButton href="/contact" label="Book a Consultation" variant="primary" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</RealestateLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-xl);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .about-hero__content {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .about-hero__photo {
    width: 280px;
    height: 280px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    object-fit: cover;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .about-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .about-hero__title {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .about-hero__brokerage {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .about-body {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .about-body__content {
    max-width: 36rem;
  }

  .about-body__content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about-body__content h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .about-cta {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about-hero__content {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-hero__photo {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
    }
  }
</style>
